---
import ContentPageLayout from '../../layouts/ContentPageLayout.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'CollectionPage',
  name: 'Printable Tree Activities',
  url: 'https://treespuzzle.com/printables/',
};
---

<ContentPageLayout
  title="Printable Tree Activities | Trees Puzzle Worksheets and Game Cards"
  heading="Printable Tree Activities"
  description="A launch-ready resource page for printable tree worksheets, leaf matching cards, bark rubbings, and forest scavenger hunt prompts."
  canonicalPath="/printables/"
  schemas={[schema]}
>
  <p>This page is structured as the resource hub for future downloads on Trees Puzzle. It gives visitors a clear place to find printable materials instead of scattering them across articles.</p>
  <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white pt-4">Planned printable formats</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
    <li>Leaf silhouette matching cards</li>
    <li>Tree observation journals</li>
    <li>Bark texture rub-and-guess sheets</li>
    <li>Forest scavenger hunt checklists</li>
    <li>Seasonal tree comparison worksheets</li>
  </ul>
  <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white pt-4">How this page supports growth</h2>
  <p>You can later attach PDFs, email signup forms, or premium bundles here without changing the rest of the site structure. That makes this a strong monetization and lead-generation page for the domain.</p>
  <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white pt-4">Recommended next additions</h2>
  <p>Add one free worksheet first, then expand with themed bundles such as autumn leaves, evergreen identification, and schoolyard scavenger packs.</p>
</ContentPageLayout>
